snippet: Befitting a workhorse who carried out 341 engagements last year, Elizabeth kicked off celebrations on Wednesday in a dutiful display.
abstract: Queen Elizabeth II kicks off her 90th birthday celebrations by observing workers at Royal Mail delivery center; activities commemorating her birth will not be limited to current week, as event is also celebrated in June for ceremonial reasons.
